General.Name: Fastighetsbolaget Emilshus AB Pfd
General.Description: Fastighetsbolaget Emilshus AB (publ) acquires, develops, and manages commercial real estate properties in Sweden. It offers its properties for industry, warehouse, industrial service/professional trade, external and grocery trade, and community service and office purposes. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Vetlanda, Sweden.
